            <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
          <a class="comment-time" href="/comment/19517510">2009-11-03 15:00:56</a>
          <span class="comment-location"></span>
        </span>
      </h3>
      <p class="comment-content">
      
        <span class="short">我是觉得入门的话太繁琐了，讲了太多各种相机、镜头、不同胶片的知识。现在毕竟是数码时代了，如果是入门的话，光圈、焦距、快门加上丰富的构图知识可能会更好。完全个人观点。</span>
      </p>
        <div class="report-comment" data-url="https://book.douban.com/subject/1007928/?comment_id=19517510"></div>
    </div>
  </li>

          
  <li class="comment-item" data-cid="411382962">
